### 1. Test Server Berjalan
GET http://localhost:5000/health

### 2. Login sebagai Admin
# Response akan mengembalikan token JWT. Salin token tersebut!
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "admin123"
}

### 3. Login sebagai Kasir
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "kasir",
  "password": "kasir123"
}

### 4. Melihat Daftar Makanan (Public)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/foods

### 5. Melihat Daftar Promo (Public)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/promos

### 6. Membuat Pesanan (Public)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "table_number": "Meja 12",
  "items": [
    {
      "food_id": 1,
      "qty": 2,
      "notes": "Tidak pedas"
    }
  ],
  "promo_code": "WEEKEND10"
}
